## What NOT to do

- Do not add `'use client'` to `page.js` — this must be a Server Component
- Do not use the anon Supabase client on this page — anonymous visitors are blocked by RLS, always use the service role client
- Do not log the tap event client-side — it fires server-side before HTML is rendered
- Do not log tap events for inactive cards
- Do not store raw IP addresses — always hash first using `hashIp()`
- Do not use a raw `<img>` tag for the profile photo — use Next.js `<Image>`
- Do not use an `<iframe>` anywhere on this page
- Do not install a vCard generation library — build the `.vcf` string manually
- Do not add any navigation, sidebar, or header chrome — this is a fully standalone page
- Do not skip the deduplication check — same IP tapping the same card within 5 minutes must only count as one tap
- Do not forget `rel="noopener noreferrer"` on all external links